    pair_with_planet_slug: 'jupiter',
    pair_with_chakra: 'Solar plexus — the seat of the young-storm-king\'s power, of the single-combat-victory, of the cosmic-warrior whose fire-center founded the ordered cosmos out of the defeated chaos; Marduk owns the *founder-and-warrior-and-king* register.',
