      'Where has my own *šarur-sentient-mace* started giving its own orders — what trusted-instrument (a habit, an automation, a system, a relationship-pattern) has *become autonomous of me* and is *making decisions I no longer control*, and is the Lugal-e warning that the mace-can-speak-for-itself already present?',
